<h1>The Stanton System</h1>
<p>Stanton is the corporate heart of the UEE. Four privately owned planets, four corporations, four visions of humanity under profit.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href={`${base}stanton/hurston/`}>Hurston — The Polluted Super-Earth</a></li>
